				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "c7420df8-b996-40a4-ba1a-c45df6284887")
	)
	(text "This is the pulse-width modulation (PWM) driver \nto actuate the magnetic coil arrays for the aerial \nrobotics platform. To achieve the required \nmagnetic field strength, the system was specified \nto drive a continuous current of 2 A per coil at \na nominal voltage of 12 V. Consequently, to \nsupport the four-coil cluster architecture, each \ndriver unit was engineered to sustain an \naggregate continuous current load of 8 A."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.494 264.16 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.8 1.8)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "d5eb06d2-34b1-40e9-aa74-e2ab7ad03476")
	)
